Red LED: 1.on if power OK 2.flashes if the power drops below about 4.63V
Green LED: 1.irregular flashes for SD card access

poweroff : 'sudo halt', 'sudo shutdown -h now' + pull the plug after green light stop flashing
reboot : 'sudo reboot', 'sudo shutdow -r now'

ssh : 'ssh pi@[ipaddress]', 'ssh pi@raspberrypi.local'(in the same network)
